sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Admin
  participant Dashboard as Admin Dashboard
  participant Gateway as API Gateway
  participant Services as Business Services
  participant Prometheus as Prometheus
  participant Loki as Loki / Logs
  participant Grafana as Grafana
  Admin->>Dashboard: Open dashboard or reports
  Dashboard->>Gateway: GET /api/admin/dashboard
  Gateway->>Services: Collect ride, driver, payment, wallet KPIs
  Services-->>Gateway: Aggregated operational data
  Gateway-->>Dashboard: Dashboard payload
  Dashboard->>Prometheus: Query service/container metrics
  Prometheus-->>Dashboard: Time-series metrics
  Dashboard->>Loki: Query application logs
  Loki-->>Dashboard: Log entries
  opt Open full monitoring view
    Dashboard->>Grafana: Open dashboard link
    Grafana-->>Admin: Visualize metrics and logs
  end
  Dashboard-->>Admin: Show KPIs, charts, and degraded services
